# DUADP Reference Node Workspace Rules

1. Do NOT use CommonJS. This project uses pure ESM (`"type": "module"`). Always use `.js` extensions in local relative imports.
2. Whenever modifying API responses, ensure they match the corresponding `duadp-*.schema.json` format in `duadp/spec/schemas/`.
3. Use `import type` for type-only imports.
4. Document all new endpoints in `duadp.org/app/page.tsx` and `llms.txt`.
5. Run `npm run build` after any TypeScript modifications to ensure types check out before notifying the user.
